div.div:
Create 10098.mcp-client.yml
Adding a collection config for model context protocol (MCP) client repos that I aggregated from these sources: - https://www.pulsemcp.com/clients - https://github.com/punkpeye/awesome-mcp-clients - https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/modelcontextprotocol/blob/main/docs/clients.mdx - https://glama.ai/mcp/clients

Add express dependency and update Vercel configuration for API routing
This commit adds the `express` package to the project, enhancing server capabilities for handling requests. Additionally, the Vercel configuration is updated to route requests to the new API entry point at `/api/index.js`, ensuring proper integration with the serverless deployment setup.

Remove unused dependencies and add Vercel configuration for serverless deployment
This commit removes the `express`, `vike-server`, and `vike-vercel` dependencies from the project, streamlining the package management. Additionally, a new `vercel.json` file is introduced to configure serverless function deployment, ensuring proper routing to the server entry point. The Vite configuration is also updated to exclude the `vike-vercel` plugin, reflecting the changes in the project structure.
